      "text": "Map<Expense,String> filter(List<Expense> expenses){\n    \n    for(Expense expense: expenses){\n            if(e follows rule1) {...}\n            else if(e follows rule 2) {...}\n            else if(e follows rule 3) {...}\n    ...\n    }\n\n}",
