      "updated": 1774194198717,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. Composition: It's a tight and a strong form of association, one class contains object of another class\n        \n\n    class -> ApiClass -> Purpose of the class is to make HTTP api request to a 3rd party services \n\n\n\nclass ApiClass{\n\n    private Retrofit client;\n}\n\nComposition is referred to be a has a relationship\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. Composition: It's a tight and a strong form of association, one class contains object of another class\n        \n\n    class -> ApiClass -> Purpose of the class is to make HTTP api request to a 3rd party services \n\n\n\nclass ApiClass{\n\n    private Retrofit client;\n}\n\nComposition is referred to be a has a relationship\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
